inlinevirtual

Advertises a service.

Uses the member node_handle_ to advertise a service, reginstering a callback method on a specific object. The services are kept inside the RosProxy object, in the services_ vector member.

Parameters
serviceThe path of the service to be advertised,
callbThe callback function to be called after a service request
objThe object, upon which the callback function should be called
